<task id="installation-instructions-all-platforms">
  <title>All Platforms Installation</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Installation <indexterm>all platforms version</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <context>The following steps describe the installation procedure of <ph keyref="product"/>,
      valid for all supported platforms:</context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Create a folder named <ph product="editor">
            <filepath>oxygen</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="author">
            <filepath>oxygenAuthor</filepath>
          </ph><ph product="developer">
            <filepath>oxygenDeveloper</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="diff">
            <filepath>diffFiles</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="svnClient">
            <filepath>syncroSVNClient</filepath>
          </ph> on your local disk.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>In the <ph product="editor">
            <filepath>oxygen</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="author">
            <filepath>oxygenAuthor</filepath>
          </ph><ph product="developer">
            <filepath>oxygenDeveloper</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="diff">
            <filepath>diffFiles</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="svnClient">
            <filepath>syncroSVNClient</filepath>
          </ph> folder, create a child folder named after the version number of <ph keyref="product"
          />.</cmd>
        <stepresult> The directory structure is <ph product="editor"> /../oxygen/<ph
              conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minorVersion"/>/ </ph>
          <ph product="author"> /../oxygenAuthor/<ph
              conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minorVersion"/>/
            </ph><ph product="developer"> /../oxygenDeveloper/<ph
              conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minorVersion"/>/ </ph>
          <ph product="diff"> /../diffFiles/<ph
              conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minorVersion"/>/ </ph>
          <ph product="svnClient"> /../syncroSVNClient/<ph
              conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minorVersion"/>/
          </ph>.</stepresult>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Download the All Platforms Installation package (<ph product="editor"
              ><filepath>oxygen.tar.gz</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="author">
            <filepath>oxygenAuthor.tar.gz</filepath>
          </ph><ph product="developer">
            <filepath>oxygenDeveloper.tar.gz</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="diff">
            <filepath>oxygenXMLDiff.tar.gz</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="svnClient">
            <filepath>syncroSVNClient.tar.gz</filepath>
          </ph>) to this folder.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Extract the archive to the same folder.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>From a command line, run the following scripts: <ph product="editor">
            <filepath>oxygen.bat</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="author">
            <filepath>oxygenAuthor.bat</filepath>
          </ph><ph product="developer">
            <filepath>oxygenDeveloper.bat</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="diff">
            <filepath>diffFiles.bat or diffDirs.bat</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="svnClient">
            <filepath>syncroSVNClient.bat</filepath>
          </ph> on Windows, <ph product="editor">
            <filepath>oxygenMac.sh</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="author">
            <filepath>oxygenAuthorMac.sh</filepath>
          </ph><ph product="developer">
            <filepath>oxygenDeveloperMac.sh</filepath></ph>
          <ph product="diff">
            <filepath>diffFilesMac.sh or diffDirsMac.sh</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="svnClient">
            <filepath>syncroSVNClientMac.sh</filepath>
          </ph> on Mac OS X, and <ph product="editor">
            <filepath>oxygen.sh</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="author">
            <filepath>oxygenAuthor.sh</filepath>
          </ph><ph product="developer">
            <filepath>oxygenDeveloper.sh</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="diff">
            <filepath>diffFiles.sh or diffDirs.sh</filepath>
          </ph>
          <ph product="svnClient">
            <filepath>syncroSVNClient.sh</filepath>
          </ph> on Unix / Linux.</cmd>
        <info>
          <note>
            <p>To change the version of the Java Virtual Machine that runs <ph keyref="product"/>,
              go to the Java command at the end of the script file and specify the full path to the
              Java executable of the desired JVM version, for example:
              <screen xml:space="preserve">"C:\Program Files\Java\jre<ph conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minimumJavaVersion"/>\bin\java" -Xmx256m -Dsun.java2d.noddraw=true ...</screen>
              on Windows,
              or<screen product="editor" xml:space="preserve">/System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/<ph conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minimumJavaVersion"/>/Home/bin/java "-Xdock:name=Oxygen" ...</screen><screen product="author" xml:space="preserve">/System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/<ph conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minimumJavaVersion"/>/Home/bin/java "-Xdock:name=Author" ...</screen><screen product="developer" xml:space="preserve">/System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/<ph conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minimumJavaVersion"/>/Home/bin/java "-Xdock:name=Developer" ...</screen><screen product="diff" xml:space="preserve">/System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/<ph conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minimumJavaVersion"/>/Home/bin/java "-Xdock:name=DiffFiles" ...</screen><screen product="svnClient" xml:space="preserve">/System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/<ph conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minimumJavaVersion"/>/Home/bin/java "-Xdock:name=SyncroSVNClient" ...</screen>
              on Mac OS X.</p>
          </note>
          <note type="important">
            <p>A Java virtual machine version <ph
                conref="../topics/oxygenEntitiesDictionary.dita#OxygenEntities/minimumJavaVersion"/>
              or later has to be installed.</p>
          </note>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Copy to clipboard the license key you have received by email and paste it in the
          application license dialog.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
